OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FA series of previously top-secret
OL,7,Ffiles relating to sightings of
OL,8,Funidentified anomalous phenomena, or
OL,9,FUAPs, sightings has been released to
OL,10,Fthe public by the Pentagon for the
OL,11,Ffirst time.
OL,13,FThe documents, shared on the
OL,14,FDepartment of War's website, concern
OL,15,Funresolved cases about which the US
OL,16,Fgovernment has been unable to make a
OL,17,F"definitive determination".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
