FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FOne such case describes an ellipsoid
OL,7,Fbronze metallic object "materialising
OL,8,Fout of a bright light in the sky" 130
OL,9,Fto 195ft in the air, before
OL,10,Fdisappearing instantly in September
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FAnother contains archival images from
OL,14,Fthe 1972 Apollo 17 mission to the
OL,15,FMoon, which show three lights visible
OL,16,Fabove the lunar terrain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump decided to
OL,7,Fprovide "maximum transparency to the
OL,8,Fpublic" so that they can "ultimately
OL,9,Fmake up their own minds" about the
OL,10,Finformation, the Pentagon said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,F"No other president or administration
OL,14,Fin history has followed through on
OL,15,Fthis level of Unidentified Anomalous
OL,16,FPhenomena (UAP) transparency," it read.
OL,18,FAdditional files will be released on a
OL,19,Frolling basis as they are discovered
OL,20,Fand declassified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,F"This is an unprecedented, historic
OL,7,Fundertaking that requires coordination
OL,8,Fbetween dozens of agencies and the
OL,9,Freview of tens of millions of records,
OL,10,Fmany existing only on paper, spanning
OL,11,Fmany decades," the Pentagon said.
OL,13,FAs well as images, the site includes
OL,14,FPDF documents of investigative
OL,15,Frecords, eyewitness testimonies, and
OL,16,Fpublic reports concerning UFOs and
OL,17,F"flying discs" dating back to the
OL,18,F1940s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FIncidents shared on the site have been
OL,7,Flogged from multiple countries,
OL,8,Fincluding the US, Syria, Iraq, Germany
OL,9,Fand the Netherlands - and even the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FThe US is currently locked in a battle
OL,13,Fwith Iran over the essential oil
OL,14,Fwaterway, which has been essentially
OL,15,Fclosed since Trump declared war on the
OL,16,Fcountry on February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FDefence secretary Pete Hegseth said
OL,7,Fthe Pentagon was aligned with Trump in
OL,8,Fwanting to bring the public
OL,9,F"unprecedented transparency" regarding
OL,10,Fthe government's understanding of UFOs.
OL,12,F"These files, hidden behind
OL,13,Fclassifications, have long fuelled
OL,14,Fjustified speculation - and it's time
OL,15,Fthe American people see it for
OL,16,Fthemselves," Hegseth said.
OL,18,F"This release of declassified
OL,19,Fdocuments demonstrates the Trump
OL,20,FAdministration's earnest commitment to
OL,21,Funprecedented transparency."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
