FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778278271
OL,3,CTop secret files about UFO sightings
OL,4,Creleased by US for first time
OL,6,FAll of the files have been reviewed
OL,7,Ffor security purposes, the Department
OL,8,Fof War said.
OL,10,F"At Nasa, our job is to bring the
OL,11,Fbrightest minds and most advanced
OL,12,Fscientific instruments to bear, follow
OL,13,Fthe data, and share what we learn,"
OL,14,Fsaid Nasa Administrator Jared Isaacman.
OL,16,F"We will remain candid about what we
OL,17,Fknow to be true, what we have yet to
OL,18,Funderstand, and all that remains to be
OL,19,Fdiscovered."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
